Actually, the reason I came here...

292
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,039
...is because I heard Brother Minjiang mention it

293
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,240
So...

294
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,360
...I wanted to do Brother Minjiang a favor

295
00:11:50,399 --> 00:11:51,720
No matter who it's for...

296
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,279
...I still need to thank you

297
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:54,440
I thought you were going to say...

298
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,600
...that feelings and work are two different things

299
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,000
You know...

300
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,399
...I like Brother Minjiang

301
00:11:59,799 --> 00:12:00,600
So...

302
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:02,639
...I thought you wouldn't want to accept my help

303
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:04,159
You didn't go back to your factory...

304
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:05,840
...but came straight here for a site visit

305
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:08,159
That shows you are a very rational person

306
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:10,799
It also means if my product is good...

307
00:12:10,799 --> 00:12:12,240
...then I still have a chance

308
00:12:12,759 --> 00:12:13,960
As for Zheng Minjiang...

309
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:16,200
...who he likes is his business

310
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,159
That has nothing to do with us making vinegar...

311
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:18,840
...or running the factory

312
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:21,039
Alright

313
00:12:21,039 --> 00:12:22,200
Let's look at other places

314
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,279
You lead the way

315
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,000
Okay

316
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,720
Wang Yingrong, I'm going to run you over!

317
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,200
Who told you to harm my son!

318
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,600
Zhen Zhen!

319
00:12:33,639 --> 00:12:35,159
How did I hit Zhen Zhen?

320
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:36,600
What are you standing there for?

321
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,480
Come here!

322
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,399
Zhen Zhen!

323
00:12:39,799 --> 00:12:40,480
Zhen Zhen!

324
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,159
How did I end up hitting you?

325
00:12:42,159 --> 00:12:43,200
Quick!

326
00:12:43,840 --> 00:12:44,639
Hurry up!

327
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,519
Zhen Zhen!

328
00:12:46,639 --> 00:12:48,840
Are you okay, Zhen Zhen?

329
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:50,600
Don't lift your leg

330
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:03,799
She...

331
00:13:03,879 --> 00:13:06,080
...will she be okay?

332
00:13:06,080 --> 00:13:07,080
She will be

333
00:13:07,399 --> 00:13:09,480
She can be treated once we get to the hospital

334
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:10,759
I...

335
00:13:10,919 --> 00:13:11,720
I...

336
00:13:12,679 --> 00:13:13,480
I...

337
00:13:15,519 --> 00:13:16,320
Auntie Chen

338
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,759
Are you tired?

339
00:13:17,799 --> 00:13:18,879
Why don't you go rest?

340
00:13:18,879 --> 00:13:20,080
I'll take her there first

341
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,120
Auntie Chen

342
00:13:26,559 --> 00:13:27,360
Auntie Chen
